<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5742865">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5742865/" class="title-link">乏善可陈！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5742865"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/barbiemonkey/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u63448969-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/barbiemonkey/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">芭比猴子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-01-16"
      class="main-meta">2013-01-16 11:06:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5742865_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  作者笔法很稚嫩，理论的部分又不严谨。   书的开头反复提到《致命ID》我就看不下去了。《致命ID》是电影，只是个编剧随手捏来的故事。用这来举例到底有什么意义？   书中的很多案例都真假难辨。像是很多个D，戴假发的发发，等等。没有出处，没有背景，这是作者自编的，还是确有...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5742865/#comments">(110回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">166有用 / 26没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5742865_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5742865_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5441677">
        

